Santa Clara past Nordhoff, 61-35. In another Frontier League game, Moorpark 
beat Calabasas, 66-47. . . . In Golden League games, Littlerock beat Burroughs 
Ridgecrest, 46-42, and Palmdale defeated Highland, 63-57. . . . St. Monica 
defeated Bell-Jeff, 67-53 in a Camino Real League game. . . . In Channel League 
