<HEADLINE>
<P>
ART REVIEW; HEADLESS FIGURES ARE SLIM SAMPLING OF POWERFUL WORK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LEAH OLLMAN, SPECIAL TO THE TIMES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
