further notice. Other centers will be opened in coming days. Those who have 
suffered losses may obtain local, state and federal assistance by visiting the 
center nearest them. Programs are being offered to cover earthquake losses to 
homes, personal property, and businesses not covered by insurance or other aid 
programs. 
