<P>
U.S. SOCCER TEAM FACES SWITZERLAND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JULIE CART 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The U.S. national soccer team will play host to the national team of 
Switzerland at noon today at Cal State Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
 The United States defeated Norway last week, 2-1, coming from behind in the 
second half. 
</P>
<P>
 The Swiss have brought a strong but not fully fit team, because most teams in 
the Swiss leagues are on an extended winter break. JULIE CART 
