</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 University of Colorado President Judith Albino survived an ouster attempt by 
members of the faculty and administration. 
</P>
<P>
 The Board of Regents voted 5-4 late Thursday to keep Albino, but will examine 
the issue again this summer. 
</P>
<P>
