<TEXT>
<P>
 A Malaysian bus driver was fired after he refused to cut his nearly six-inch 
fingernails. 
</P>
<P>
 Malaysia's road department told Jaafar Nordin that the fingernails not only 
look bad but could hinder his driving. When Nordin refused to cut them, the 
