<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 22, 1994, Saturday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 2; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
